<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Phishing Email Challenge - Virtual Office</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header class="app-header">
        <div class="header-content">
            <h1>Virtual Office Inbox</h1>
            <div class="game-stats">
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                    Score: <span id="score">0</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-level-up-alt"></i>
                    Level: <span id="level">1</span>
                </div>
                <div class="stat-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-clock"></i>
                    Time: <span id="timer">5:00</span>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>

    <div class="main-container">
        <aside class="sidebar">
            <div class="game-progress">
                <h3>Level Progress</h3>
                <div class="progress-bar">
                    <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 0%"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="game-tips">
                <h3>Security Tips</h3>
                <ul id="security-tips">
                    <li>Check sender's email address carefully</li>
                    <li>Be wary of urgent or threatening language</li>
                    <li>Hover over links before clicking</li>
                    <li>Watch for spelling and grammar errors</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main>
            <div id="email-list">
                <p>Loading emails...</p>
            </div>

            <div id="email-details" class="hidden">
                <div class="email-full-header">
                    <h2>Email Details</h2>
                    <p><strong>From:</strong> <span id="email-sender"></span> (<span id="email-address"></span>)</p>
                    <p><strong>Subject:</strong> <span id="email-subject"></span></p>
                    <p><strong>Date:</strong> <span id="email-date"></span></p>
                </div>
                <div id="email-body"></div>
                <div class="email-actions">
                    <button onclick="submitChoice(true)" class="btn-danger">
                        <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        Mark as Phishing
                    </button>
                    <button onclick="submitChoice(false)" class="btn-safe">
                        <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        Mark as Safe
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <div id="feedback"></div>

    <div class="attack-simulation">
        <div class="attack-content">
            <h2><i class="fas fa-virus"></i> Cyber Attack in Progress!</h2>
            <p>Oh no! That was a phishing email and you fell for it. Your system is now compromised!</p>
            <p>Learning Point: <span id="learning-point"></span></p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="level-complete hidden">
        <h2><i class="fas fa-trophy"></i> Level Complete!</h2>
        <p>Great job identifying the threats! You've earned <span id="points-earned">0</span> points.</p>
        <p>Next level will be more challenging...</p>
        <button onclick="startNextLevel()" class="btn-safe">
            <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i>
            Continue to Next Level
        </button>
    </div>

    <script src="/script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
